,\nand surface-atmosphere interactions cannot be practically made by additional\nflybys, and they cannot be made from Earth-based observations. We find that\nthese limitations, combined with Pluto's many important, open scientific\nquestions, strongly motivate a Pluto System follow on orbiter mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Aug 2018 17:20:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 16 Sep 2018 04:42:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 18:28:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2021 18:10:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-18"}
