ination of a volume type free boundary\nproblem and an obstacle type problem, hence their growth condition is\ninfluenced in a non-standard way by these two ingredients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 11:04:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Sep 2018 20:33:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2020 11:56:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-13"}
