We prove that the single-loop full\ngradient-based algorithm applied to the corresponding time-varying penalized\nproblem converges to the solution of the original constrained problem in the\ncase of the strongly convex objective function.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 13:46:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 20:55:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-04"}
