 changing the base of the $\\mathbb{Z}^2$-action through a\nshear conjugacy. Algorithms are provided to find markers, recognizable\nsubstitutions, and shear conjugacy from a set of Wang tiles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Aug 2018 15:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Apr 2019 16:13:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2019 15:45:34 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2019 14:54:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-27"}
